  "description": "Bulk mineral acids, alkalis, industrial gases, distillation infrastructure, cement production, air separation, specialty gases for semiconductor fabrication, petroleum alternatives and coal tar chemistry, lubricants and cutting fluids, and electrolytic processes. A civilization's industrial maturity can be measured by its sulfuric acid production. Provides the etchants, solvents, reagents, and purification infrastructure needed for semiconductor fabrication.",
